{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"3da79cf1c4","title":"周恩来、陈伯达、康生、江青、王力、关锋、戚本禹等接见贵州革命派代表座谈纪要","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"147d228a8b","index":0,"year":1967,"month":1,"day":28,"articleId":"3da79cf1c4","article":{}}],"tags":[{"name":"关锋","id":"00506c3c84","type":"人物"},{"name":"王力","id":"20ebde32a6","type":"人物"},{"name":"周恩来","id":"523bb79e8f","type":"人物"},{"name":"戚本禹","id":"57434e107b","type":"人物"},{"name":"康生","id":"57eea82497","type":"人物"},{"name":"江青","id":"82305e518c","type":"人物"},{"name":"周总理","id":"838b5f2c9d","type":"人物"},{"name":"文章","id":"c9f57d6426","type":"文稿类型"},{"name":"李再含","id":"d778f94355","type":"人物"},{"name":"陈伯达","id":"e46e45351b","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"GPCRv3","name":"中国文化大革命文库（第三版）","internal":true,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":"","articles":[],"comments":[],"contents":[],"pages":[]}],"authors":[{"id":"421124ccd3","name":"江青"}]},"publication_details":{"GPCRv3":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"2c5d23cfa3","type":"title","text":"周恩来、陈伯达、康生、江青、王力、关锋、戚本禹等接见贵州革命派代表座谈纪要","index":0,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"3da79cf1c4","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"064b6465c3","type":"paragraph","text":"时间： 一九六七年一月二十八日下午六时五十分至九时。","index":1,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"3da79cf1c4","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"5cd83cbd07","type":"paragraph","text":"地点： 人民大会堂。","index":2,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"3da79cf1c4","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"6833b8f8d7","type":"paragraph","text":"在座的有李成芳、李再含、何光宇等同志。","index":3,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"3da79cf1c4","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"58c6a92889","type":"paragraph","text":"李再含汇报：介绍贵阳的红卫军现在情况,谈到有人讲江青同志说红卫军是反革命组织。","index":4,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"3da79cf1c4","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"bfdd1da30b","type":"paragraph","text":"江青：现在谣言可多了。","index":5,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"3da79cf1c4","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"8307533db3","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：是反革命领导篡权,主要是头子反动,马上辟谣,有一个办法可以讲,我们反对苏修领导集团,但不反对苏联人民。","index":6,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"3da79cf1c4","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"a6d6768443","type":"paragraph","text":"李再含：红卫军内部有所分化,有反对李铁乃的,成立了造反联络站,要区别两个情况,一个方面是以李铁乃为首的反革命集团与广大红卫军战士应分开( 江青:必须 )底下一些组织已分化,应承认是革命造反派。( 江青:红卫军当然不是反革命组织,对广大群众不能这样说,主要是头头反动 )。","index":7,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"3da79cf1c4","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"c98624e4bf","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：欢迎分化,欢迎立功。","index":8,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"3da79cf1c4","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"90495d9920","type":"paragraph","text":"江青: 分化有两种:一种向左的,一种向极右的,应该区别。","index":9,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"3da79cf1c4","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"8428bf879d","type":"paragraph","text":"康生、江青: 红卫军名字相当臭,得改名字。","index":10,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"3da79cf1c4","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"c6f63bab65","type":"paragraph","text":"李再含: ( 谈到贵阳工人纠察队任意抓普通红卫军战士的情况 )。","index":11,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"3da79cf1c4","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"920998e03d","type":"paragraph","text":"江青: 把李铁乃一小撮与红卫军普通战士应该区别开来,这也是毛主席一贯思想, 全国范围的红旗军、红卫军、捍卫团、赤卫军这些名字臭死了,分化出去要改名字。","index":12,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"3da79cf1c4","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"957ca0a547","type":"paragraph","text":"何光宇: ( 谈到红卫军分化情况,并谈到有一小撮人讲:逮捕李铁乃一小撮是军区和公安厅搞的阴谋,要冲军区。)","index":13,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"3da79cf1c4","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"051b0f3ebc","type":"paragraph","text":"江青: 唬人。","index":14,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"3da79cf1c4","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"1969d8eae7","type":"paragraph","text":"李再含、何光字：有人保李铁乃,有几百人游行,准备冲军区( 并谈了逮捕红旗军情况)。","index":15,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"3da79cf1c4","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"0df6288e17","type":"paragraph","text":"总理: ( 一个个介绍了贵州革命派十一人及所代表的革命组织 )。","index":16,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"3da79cf1c4","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"271f63b546","type":"paragraph","text":"江青：没有女将,应该有女的,大男子主义（众笑笑)。红卫军这个名字太长,别人记不到,红卫军名字要改一改,当然对红卫军战士不能象对待李铁乃那样。","index":17,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"3da79cf1c4","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"c3acdd702e","type":"paragraph","text":"陈伯达：清一色。","index":18,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"3da79cf1c4","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"5727d98078","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：那倒不一定。","index":19,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"3da79cf1c4","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"c7fc49be88","type":"paragraph","text":"你们两个文件都传着看了,想研究一下,明天再座谈这个问题。五个原则( 按：对当权派处理的原则 ) ,抓一批、罢一批、调一批、提一批、留一批的方针是对的。这五项原则是好的。","index":20,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"3da79cf1c4","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"1b2324923c","type":"paragraph","text":"( 首长又问: 你们夺了权以后怎么办? )","index":21,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"3da79cf1c4","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"29ff3bbc98","type":"paragraph","text":"代表：来之前有些准备,我们离开时夺的权（ 接着谈了些考虑 )。","index":22,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"3da79cf1c4","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"10f0141cec","type":"paragraph","text":"陈伯达：回去研究,再交上来。","index":23,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"3da79cf1c4","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"9752675030","type":"paragraph","text":"代表: (谈三个机构问题,当前有些组织机构庞杂,谈到红卫军庞大总部时)。 总理：新的官僚机构,就象个省委机构。","index":24,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"3da79cf1c4","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"9490984b84","type":"paragraph","text":"代表: ( 谈关于公安机关保卫文化大革命的组织形式)。","index":25,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"3da79cf1c4","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"5bade548ec","type":"paragraph","text":"江青：监督小组就是改革,成立保卫委员会是革命。","index":26,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"3da79cf1c4","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"9b3e7a2e32","type":"paragraph","text":"代表: ( 谈到三权问题 )。","index":27,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"3da79cf1c4","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"6fa6d75c89","type":"paragraph","text":"江青. 三个权,还有一个军权,军队不是和你们站在一起了吗?","index":28,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"3da79cf1c4","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"ef63e02b28","type":"paragraph","text":"代表: ( 谈到生产情况和外出串连情况 )。","index":29,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"3da79cf1c4","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"bfbc0b3333","type":"paragraph","text":"江青:下命令叫回去,限日子。不回去就开除（ 指内迁工人返回原地 )。","index":30,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"3da79cf1c4","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"c2e1782bb3","type":"paragraph","text":"代表: ( 谈了贵阳目前斗争形势和政治力量,走资本主义道路当权派情况,阶线斗争很复杂时)。","index":31,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"3da79cf1c4","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"bb07ea4b46","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：你们把贾启允软禁了吗?","index":32,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"3da79cf1c4","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"25bc4953bc","type":"paragraph","text":"江青：城市街道怎么样,你们要摸点经验。","index":33,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"3da79cf1c4","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"5219798976","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：官僚、地主都在街道上。","index":34,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"3da79cf1c4","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"bd60d51324","type":"paragraph","text":"江青：这次要横扫。","index":35,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"3da79cf1c4","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"6f088a8859","type":"paragraph","text":"代表: ( 谈到工人纠察队情况 )。","index":36,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"3da79cf1c4","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"14142a1034","type":"paragraph","text":"江青：工人纠察队,是不是凌驾其他组织之上,象北京东城西城纠察队一样。 代表: ( 又谈当前工人纠察队的活跃情况 )。","index":37,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"3da79cf1c4","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"ca5b6b3d37","type":"paragraph","text":"江青: 纠察队要死灰复燃。","index":38,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"3da79cf1c4","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"31fbd6c682","type":"paragraph","text":"周总理与康生同志拉话：所有工会都是保守派的大本营,他们有钱有房子。 江青：钱还不是国家的钱,真够呛。","index":39,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"3da79cf1c4","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"5c2b1f8a60","type":"paragraph","text":"( 代表们又谈到红卫军基层问题 )。","index":40,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"3da79cf1c4","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"347ac1af1a","type":"paragraph","text":"关锋: ( 谈苏联二月革命,布尔什维克、孟什维克的关系 )。","index":41,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"3da79cf1c4","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"a0e4cdf43d","type":"paragraph","text":"江青：那天晚上来三个人,李铁乃威胁我、陈伯达、康生要接见他,不见立刻要走。走就走。我们就是不接见。后来一查，还是没走,后来怕他跑,赶快把他抓起来。","index":42,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"3da79cf1c4","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"280241f420","type":"paragraph","text":"康生：一般军字号都是有问题的。","index":43,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"3da79cf1c4","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"cd202976e0","type":"paragraph","text":"江青: 可以改为工人控诉造反团。李铁乃原是什么人?","index":44,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"3da79cf1c4","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"0865038f46","type":"paragraph","text":"( 何光宇和代表介绍了情况 )","index":45,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"3da79cf1c4","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"f564893d32","type":"paragraph","text":"江青:李铁乃是流氓,他想当西南王。对李铁乃一小撮,与广大红卫军不同,红卫军的名字臭透了,一定要改,西南王是流氓。","index":46,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"3da79cf1c4","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"73b680c7b0","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：他有五个秘书,我才五个秘书。","index":47,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"3da79cf1c4","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"7d17b1a39a","type":"paragraph","text":"代表: ( 谈省委常委开会情况 )。","index":48,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"3da79cf1c4","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"c50b88130a","type":"paragraph","text":"江青：他们还在开会?这样还能工作。你们要回去,脱离太久太危险,一天几次大变。","index":49,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"3da79cf1c4","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"0b38105cd1","type":"paragraph","text":"陈伯达:你们回去宣布,昨天李铁乃又来了四个人,又抓起来了,我叫人抓的。 你们回去赶快自己开会,在控诉团上做文章,名字改一下,叫工人革命造反团,你们就会主动,就不会被保字号利用。","index":50,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"3da79cf1c4","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"e69073cc39","type":"paragraph","text":"戚本禹：你们和群众商量商量。","index":51,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"3da79cf1c4","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"69c68ee0bd","type":"paragraph","text":"江青：这样就把大多数争取过来了,不然被保字号利用。","index":52,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"3da79cf1c4","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"29d9584cf4","type":"paragraph","text":"康生：从全国讲,军字号不高明。","index":53,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"3da79cf1c4","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"76e756d008","type":"paragraph","text":"陈伯达: 红旗军的问题有反革命背景,他们抽香烟是中华牌,吃罐头,用钱如流水。","index":54,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"3da79cf1c4","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"60ad8df1e3","type":"paragraph","text":"江青：很可能与外国有联系。","index":55,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"3da79cf1c4","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"c0f7c22aa0","type":"paragraph","text":"康生: 你们文件总的精神是好的,文字上要修改,有些重复。注意革命有曲折,有几个回合。","index":56,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"3da79cf1c4","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"2fae263c41","type":"paragraph","text":"陈伯达：你们回去好好搞,可以成为革命模范省,做群众工作,团结大多数,对保字派分化,瓦解他们,捍卫团正土崩瓦解。","index":57,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"3da79cf1c4","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"0ba3cc9e81","type":"paragraph","text":"王力: 红卫军有所不同,基层组织有很多是很好的,是起作用的。","index":58,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"3da79cf1c4","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"20730e8efd","type":"paragraph","text":"关锋：对红卫军底下不是分化瓦解的问题,是要造李铁乃的反的问题。","index":59,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"3da79cf1c4","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"ce06b68331","type":"paragraph","text":"伯达：具体问题具体分析,掌握毛主席的战略和策略,要争取大多数群众，要争取动摇不定分子。","index":60,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"3da79cf1c4","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"f89392dd19","type":"paragraph","text":"康生：北京有个经验,左派要团结。左派内部夺权后不团结相互吵架,你夺我的权,我夺你的权。","index":61,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"3da79cf1c4","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"4df9d8da81","type":"paragraph","text":"伯达：要照顾大局。","index":62,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"3da79cf1c4","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"f60a0c084a","type":"paragraph","text":"康生：要协商,小团体主义,宗派主义,风头主义都要注意。左派存在这个毛病,尤其是夺权以后,这个问题带有普遍性,北京、上海、哈尔滨都有这个问题。","index":63,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"3da79cf1c4","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"c07f70c17d","type":"paragraph","text":"王力：革命派夺权以后,地位变化了,有出现争权夺利的情况,这是小资产阶级、农民意识反映到革命队伍中。","index":64,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"3da79cf1c4","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"fed6193cba","type":"paragraph","text":"伯达：今天我到一个工厂去,少数派变为多数,矛盾就多了,要注意。","index":65,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"3da79cf1c4","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"7eb391d57f","type":"paragraph","text":"康生：你们（代表团中的）北大、清华要起这个作用,把大多数团结起来（指学生代表) ,工人纠察队不可怕,李铁乃不可怕，可怕的是内部不团结。","index":66,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"3da79cf1c4","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"07f4842bfc","type":"paragraph","text":"伯达:夺权了要特别注意,否则会走向反面,走资本主义道路的当权派会看笑话。","index":67,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"3da79cf1c4","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"ef8ebd6b6c","type":"paragraph","text":"康生：沿这个道路走下来,左派会成右派,搞不好会垮台的，今天重新发表主席的 \"古田会议\"的文章,你们要好好学。","index":68,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"3da79cf1c4","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"281a6c7759","type":"paragraph","text":"关锋：要为无产阶级而夺权,不能为个人夺权,为小集团夺权,否则会走反面。 伯达：是整个阶级的夺权!","index":69,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"3da79cf1c4","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"1d129ec799","type":"paragraph","text":"康生: (对学生代表)你们三司有人搞突出,考虑名字排在前面后面的。","index":70,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"3da79cf1c4","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"034c378442","type":"paragraph","text":"代表：底下同志对上面要有意见。","index":71,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"3da79cf1c4","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"2cba0ea4a4","type":"paragraph","text":"伯达: 不要象马铃薯、山药蛋一个一个的,要团结起来!","index":72,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"3da79cf1c4","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"b31ae25e20","type":"paragraph","text":"（ 代表向首长表示态度 )。","index":73,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"3da79cf1c4","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"4abe0d5360","type":"paragraph","text":"伯达：要好好团结,吸取教训。","index":74,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"3da79cf1c4","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"420d1bf401","type":"paragraph","text":"代表：贵州人民非常渴望见到毛主席和中央首长。","index":75,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"3da79cf1c4","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"98012da80f","type":"paragraph","text":"( 代表们介绍了纪念遵义会议三十二周年大会群众参加的情况 )。","index":76,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"3da79cf1c4","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"38ee7c304a","type":"paragraph","text":"康生：一定要作革命的左派,就能见到,以后一定要见的。","index":77,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"3da79cf1c4","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"481480f4f1","type":"paragraph","text":"来源：邓振新编著《贵州风云》(香港：中国国际文艺出版社，2014)。","index":78,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"3da79cf1c4","publication":{},"article":{}}],"page":{"start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}